item.title: MSAIL TECH TALK w/ Wesley Tian
item.description:
University of Michigan alumni and former MSAIL member Wesley Tian, the Co-founder and CEO of Aragon.ai, will talk about his journey, share what he learned from starting his AI company, and offer career advice.

RSVP for this event here!

item.title: MSAIL TECH TALK w/ Kiran Prasad
item.description:
University of Michigan and Carnegie Mellon alumni Kiran Prasad will share his professional journey, thoughts about Grad School, and give a talk about machine learning concepts that he uses in industry. Kiran is a Senior ML Engineer at Gather, where he works on end-to-end AI system design. He previously was an Applied Scientist on the Microsoft Turing team (Microsoft’s NLP v-team that created CoPilot and spearheaded collaboration with OpenAI).

RSVP for this event here!
